Class Airplane

java.lang.Object
Airplane
public class Airplane
extends java.lang.Object
This airplane class is where all the methods that does adding a passenger, adding a group, canceling reservations, showing a manifest list, and showing availability. Also, the airplane class sets up both the first class and economy class, that are inherited from the ClassPreference class, and sets up the 2D array data structure with each seat being an object to store information.
